-- Greencoat to Buy SSE Wind Farms for 140 Million Pounds in IPO
-- B y   R e e d   L a n d b e r g
-- 2013-02-06T07:55:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-06/greencoat-to-buy-sse-wind-farms-for-140-million-pounds-in-ipo.html
Greencoat U.K. Wind Plc said it’s
seeking to make an initial public offering of shares to raise
205 million pounds for the purchase of wind farms from the
British utility SSE Plc.  SSE said it agreed to sell four wind farms with a combined
generation capacity of 79.5 megawatts to Greencoat for 140
million pounds. The utility in a statement said it woudl invest
43 million pounds in Greencoat’s new fund, according to a
statement released today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Reed Landberg in London at 
